         MACRO ,                                       ADDED ON GP05355
&NM      ZI    &ADDRESS,&FLAGS
.*   ADDED IN RESPONSE TO A THREAD ON IBM-MAIN ABOUT RESETTING FLAGS
.*     THIS MACRO ALLOWS SPECIFICATION OF THE FLAGS TO BE RESET,
.*     INSTEAD OF THE NI CONVENTION OF ALL BUT
.*
&NM      NI    &ADDRESS,255-(&FLAGS)
         MEND  ,
